  "3227490": {
    "name": "Jumfrog",
    "steam_appid": 3227490,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227490/extras/ed34975889d5c74934af93a323753d5a.poster.avif?t=1755142676\" width=650 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227490/extras/ed34975889d5c74934af93a323753d5a.webm?t=1755142676\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227490/extras/ed34975889d5c74934af93a323753d5a.mp4?t=1755142676\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >目标</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >瞪大你的蛤蟆眼，蹦出这个阴暗的水井！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227490/extras/dfca87c8e605253361489ed3409ef6fd.poster.avif?t=1755142676\" width=204 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227490/extras/dfca87c8e605253361489ed3409ef6fd.webm?t=1755142676\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227490/extras/dfca87c8e605253361489ed3409ef6fd.mp4?t=1755142676\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227490/extras/7697815c48a7fb369a61547782e77017.poster.avif?t=1755142676\" width=204 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227490/extras/7697815c48a7fb369a61547782e77017.webm?t=1755142676\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227490/extras/7697815c48a7fb369a61547782e77017.mp4?t=1755142676\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227490/extras/ee2f1e01ed02f992e2bdcb4d27b9a675.poster.avif?t=1755142676\" width=204 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227490/extras/ee2f1e01ed02f992e2bdcb4d27b9a675.webm?t=1755142676\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227490/extras/ee2f1e01ed02f992e2bdcb4d27b9a675.mp4?t=1755142676\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>一个不含糊的平台跳跃游戏</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >没有敌人，没有死亡——只有纯粹、不掺水的挑战。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的技巧和耐心是你通往荣耀的唯一障碍。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227490/extras/85baf669db4726a44f71d78316198a2f.poster.avif?t=1755142676\" width=650 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227490/extras/85baf669db4726a44f71d78316198a2f.webm?t=1755142676\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227490/extras/85baf669db4726a44f71d78316198a2f.mp4?t=1755142676\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>看穿阴影</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在一个黑暗的世界中穿行，你的青蛙那发光的眼睛会照亮道路。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >右键点击可以向前看——那双眼睛是你可靠的向导！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227490/extras/cf1a767b424844391d641361e0955cd4.poster.avif?t=1755142676\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227490/extras/cf1a767b424844391d641361e0955cd4.webm?t=1755142676\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227490/extras/cf1a767b424844391d641361e0955cd4.mp4?t=1755142676\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>弹弓式跳跃</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >像弹弓一样向后拉然后发射你的青蛙——嘣！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过一个像素级细微变化、超过10帧的精妙控制的下蹲动作来微调你的跳跃。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可以选择短而安全的跳跃，用力拉扯进行疯狂跳跃，或者调整角度以穿过狭窄的缝隙——可能性是无限的。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >流畅的物理引擎意味着每一个微调都会改变你的命运，让你能够以十几种不同的方式挑战同一个平台。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用你的指尖描绘出数千条跳跃弧线，并实现完美的着陆。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>可爱的明星主角</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >像素艺术可爱到让你忘记自己已经摔进深渊多少次了。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一只惹人喜爱的青蛙伙伴，踏上了一场硬核冒险。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227490/extras/1d2fee6283289388e0e55964d6294dbe.poster.avif?t=1755142676\" width=616 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227490/extras/1d2fee6283289388e0e55964d6294dbe.webm?t=1755142676\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227490/extras/1d2fee6283289388e0e55964d6294dbe.mp4?t=1755142676\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>困难时就唱歌</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在挣扎中，你可以随时享受你的青蛙的“呱呱”小夜曲！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >感觉累了？唱首歌，休息一下。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >搞砸了？别担心——放松一下，重整旗鼓。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227490/extras/e81ef0bbedfb0ce53173ba545d358e96.poster.avif?t=1755142676\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227490/extras/e81ef0bbedfb0ce53173ba545d358e96.webm?t=1755142676\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3227490/extras/e81ef0bbedfb0ce53173ba545d358e96.mp4?t=1755142676\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>庆祝坠落</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >摔倒了？恭喜！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次坠落都是一场盛宴：如果你从高处跌落，彩带会爆炸，一位幽灵观察者会出现，评论你“令人印象深刻”的跳跃。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过屏幕上的高度损失标签追踪你的下落 — 因为有时候，跌得很远也值得一个专属的记分板。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>为跳跃狂热者准备的困难模式</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >觉得普通的攀登太容易？试试盲跳吧。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在困难模式中，你的手电筒消失了 — 没有预览，没有提示；只有你的记忆、本能和纯粹的技巧。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >唯一的帮助？你的青蛙自然发光稍微亮了一些……但别指望它能救你。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >只有最勇敢的青蛙才能活着逃脱。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于游戏</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎来到 JumFrog——一个充满无情挑战的游戏，即使是最小的失误也可能让你一落千丈。这可不是胆小鬼玩的游戏；这是一场残酷的技巧考验，会把你逼到极限。但是，那胜利的滋味？绝对值得你心跳加速的每一秒。每一次跳跃都惊险刺激，每一次失误都可能酿成大祸——这肾上腺素飙升的感觉绝对让你欲罢不能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但是等等，这可不仅仅是跳来跳去那么简单。这只戴着王冠的青蛙是从哪儿来的？为什么井里会下雪？这只小家伙拼命想要逃离的墙外又有什么？最重要的是——这个神秘的坑洞到底是怎么回事？系好安全带，因为这段旅程充满了问号。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏玩法</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在 JumFrog 中，每一次跳跃都是成败的关键。一个错误的动作，你所有的努力都可能瞬间白费。但别被吓跑了！每一次跌倒都是一次教训，每一次重试都是一次磨练技巧的机会。你会咒骂，你会欢呼，你会变得比以往任何时候都更强大。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >跳进来，看看你是否有能力逃离水井——或者至少弄清楚为什么会有一只戴着王冠的青蛙被困在那里！</p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语, 法语, 意大利语, 德语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 俄语, 日语, 简体中文, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 繁体中文, 土耳其语, 波兰语, 韩语",
